                    About this place
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                    Experience comfort, privacy, and a peaceful stay in this carefully curated home.
                    Perfect for solo travelers, couples, or small families looking for a memorable stay.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Highlights -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
                <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/10">
                    üè° <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Entire place</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/10">
                    üßº <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Clean & safe</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/10">
                    üåô <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Peaceful stay</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

